      <title>雅典机场股票在希腊证券交易所首次亮相</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/athens-airport-stock-rises-in-debut-on-greek-stock-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雅典国际机场股份公司 (Athens International Airport SA) 的股价在雅典证券交易所开始交易时上涨了 15%，这是该国二十多年来最大规模的首次公开募股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/athens-airport-stock-rises-in-debut-on-greek-stock-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:35:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着饮酒量的减少，嘉士伯的利润将适度增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlsberg-expects-moderate-profit-growth-as-drinkers-spend-less</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉士伯公司预计今年的营业利润将温和增长，因为一些消费者不再喝啤酒，而且该公司在营销上投入更多资金以专注于增长更快的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlsberg-expects-moderate-profit-growth-as-drinkers-spend-less</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:07:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银提供 10 亿美元的 AT1 作为其融资计划的快速启动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/ubs-offers-1-billion-at1s-in-fast-start-to-year-s-funding-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团 (UBS Group AG) 在制定未来几年增发数十亿美元风险证券的计划后一天，就发行了以美元计价的额外一级票据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/ubs-offers-1-billion-at1s-in-fast-start-to-year-s-funding-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥斯特德削减股息，首席执行官试图削减不断上升的成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/orsted-pauses-dividend-as-ceo-cuts-costs-to-avoid-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Orsted A/S 将暂停支付股息，至少到 2025 年为止，并削减本十年建设新项目的计划，作为首席执行官 Mads Nipper 概述的一系列成本削减措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/orsted-pauses-dividend-as-ceo-cuts-costs-to-avoid-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:09:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维斯塔斯表示，随着危机缓解，今年的前景正在改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/vestas-posts-improving-outlook-for-this-year-as-crisis-abates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维斯塔斯风力系统公司 (Vestas Wind Systems A/S) 预计，随着这家丹麦公司结束了导致项目开发放缓的全行业危机，在 2023 年恢复盈利后，今年的盈利将有所改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/vestas-posts-improving-outlook-for-this-year-as-crisis-abates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管利润下降，Equinor仍将向投资者支付140亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/equinor-profit-retreats-on-lower-prices-for-natural-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Equinor ASA 表示，今年将按照石油巨头当前向投资者输送剩余现金的做法，支付 140 亿美元的股票回购和股息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/equinor-profit-retreats-on-lower-prices-for-natural-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
