    <item>
      <title>穆迪将 NYCB 的信用评级下调至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/new-york-community-bancorp-s-credit-grade-cut-to-junk-by-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约社区银行 (New York Community Bancorp) 的信用评级被穆迪投资者服务公司 (Moody&#39;s Investors Service) 下调至垃圾级，不到一周后，这家地区性银行大幅削减派息并储备储备金以应对与商业房地产相关的问题贷款，从而引起了股东的警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/new-york-community-bancorp-s-credit-grade-cut-to-junk-by-moody-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 00:28:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券、股票在美联储发言人面前小幅波动：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
